		<div class="article" role="main">
			<div id="headline">
									
	<h1 class="invisible" itemprop="headline">Sunderland interim boss Kevin Ball wants to be Di Canio successor</h1>

     
         
 
								
				
				
							</div>

			    
                          <p class="introduction" id="story_continues_1" itemprop="description">    Sunderland&#039;s caretaker boss Kevin Ball has said he would like to be considered as a permanent successor to the recently sacked Paolo Di Canio. 
</p>
  
          <p>    Ball guided the Black Cats into the fourth round of the League Cup with a 
    
<a  href="http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/24122228" >2-0 win over Peterborough</a> 

     on Tuesday. 
</p>
  
    <!--  Embedding the video player -->
<!--  This is the embedded player component -->


	
 





<div class="videoInStoryC story-feature emp-no-switch">
    <div id="emp-24237450-457" class="emp">    
        		
        <noscript>
            <div class="warning">
                                <img class="holding" src="http://news.bbcimg.co.uk/media/images/70104000/jpg/_70104383_kevinball.jpg" alt="Kevin Ball" />
                                <p><strong>Please turn on JavaScript.</strong> Media requires JavaScript to play.</p>
            </div>
        </noscript>
        <object width="0" height="0">
